{"tid":230520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[移民POST] 有無已經移民既巴絲打，入來Share實況？不要鳩吹 [２]","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T14:33:23.000Z","uid":54684,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9ddad30a474fb66dc6e013f7e65c64ef67f11c","tid":230520,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"舊POST︰<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/173946/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/173946/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n拿，日日都有人話要移民<br />\nA巴打︰我3年內移民架喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nB巴打︰屌，下年就會移，HK bye bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nC巴打︰搞緊技術移民，過緊去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD巴打︰一早移左民10年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> HAHAHAHAHA........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<strong>個個都話搞緊移民<br />\n你又移民，我又移民，<br />\n搞到好似個個都移緊民<br />\n但從來無乜幾個真係開post講，<br />\n自己移完民之後，<br />\nsettle down左，真正情況係點！<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬<br />\n<ins>有無圖畀人想像下呀？</ins><br />\n你間新屋係乜撚野樣先？<br />\n一日三餐食乜撚野先？<br />\n返緊乜野工，做D乜野？<br />\n有邊幾位朋友/同事？<br />\n新家園環境係點？<br />\n有咩娛樂呀？<br />\n日常講咩語言呀？<br />\n畀多少少具體details OK？<br />\n</strong></div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n喂啊哥，圖都唔多張<br />\n個個鳩吹<br />\n一陣又話移左去台中<br />\n一陣又話走左去NZ<br />\n但圖都無張<br />\n猛鳩吹 強力鳩吹 瘋狂鳩吹<br />\n推到個Post幾十頁<br />\n都係文字直播<br />\n咁既討論，會唔會太鳩呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無圖既話，你話你10年前移左民去美國紐約靠苦幹致富，依家係摩天大廈頂樓歎緊日光浴，左手攬緊鬼妹右攬緊日本妹都得架啦！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我想知︰<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有無已經移左民既巴絲打，入來Share下實際情況</span></span></strong><br />\n老實少少，畀幾張相，講下&quot;台中新生活的日常&quot;，&quot;住左悉尼1年既日常&quot;之類<br />\n有D實質討論<br />\n好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n我畀個例子大家<br />\n以下係移民去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>紐西蘭</strong></span>既生活既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證據</span></span></strong>︰<br />\n<img src=\"http://a.bbkz.net/guide/images/5/50/%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa.bbkz.net%2Fguide%2Fimages%2F5%2F50%2F%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597.png&h=f5af8647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>黃翠如BB</strong></span>帶大家睇下，去片！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有線   地平線上這個世界那些人 黃翠如 第25集<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-7P2mrBWTfg?t=7m12s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-7P2mrBWTfg%3Ft%3D7m12s&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=52056433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-7P2mrBWTfg?t=7m12s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2017/04/03/73072_20170403010405_58e12f05c27ad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F03%2F73072_20170403010405_58e12f05c27ad.gif&h=9d04b76c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc21fe43214b42d4f9332d1ccf0046f75aefbff0","tid":230520,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":